2015年的'''[[苏丹|苏丹]]大选'''举行于4月13日－16日，选出[[苏丹总统|总统]]和[[国民议会_(苏丹)|国民议会]]成员。原定于4月2日，但推迟了11天。<ref>[http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/12/20/us-sudan-election-idUSKBN0JY0J420141220 Sudan postpones April elections by 11 days: elections committee] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/12/20/us-sudan-election-idUSKBN0JY0J420141220 |date=20150402231720 }} Reuters, 20 December 2014</ref>这是[[南苏丹|南苏丹]]分裂后举行的首次选举。<ref name ="embassy"/>

现任总统[[奥马尔·巴希尔|奥马尔·巴希尔]]（Omar al-Bashir）虽然遭到大多数党派反对抵制，仍以压倒性优势赢得总统选举。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-32481013 |title=Omar al-Bashir wins Sudan elections by a landslide |date=27 April 2015 |website= |publisher=BBC News |access-date=30 April 2015 |archive-date=2015-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150430034630/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-32481013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>执政的[[全国大会党_(苏丹)|全国大会党]]在国民议会426个席位中赢得多数。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nec.org.sd/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%A6%D8%AC-%D9%88-%D8%A7%D8%AD%D8%B5%D8%A7%D8%A6%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA-2015.pdf |title=Election results |format=PDF |date=27 April 2015 |language=ar |publisher=NEC |access-date=28 April 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518072336/http://nec.org.sd/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%A6%D8%AC-%D9%88-%D8%A7%D8%AD%D8%B5%D8%A7%D8%A6%D9%8A%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA-2015.pdf |archive-date=2015-05-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==选举制度==

使用两轮选举系统进行总统选举；如果没有候选人在第一轮获得多数的选票，将举行第二轮选举。<ref>[http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2145/ Election for President] {{Wayback|url=http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2145/ |date=20200509103204 }} IFES</ref>

三种方法选出国民议会的成员；一些成员由多数成员投票选出；全国18个州的选区选出；由比例分配一些席位。

选民投两次票。一个选政党候选人，一个投比例代表制席位<ref name=IPU>[http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2297_B.htm Electoral system] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2297_B.htm |date=20170326214620 }} IPU</ref>。

==阵营==
现任总统[[奥马尔·巴希尔|奥马尔·巴希尔]]2014年10月再次被选为[[全国大会党_(苏丹)|全国大会党]]的总统候选人<ref>[http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/10/sudan-bashir-seek-re-election-2015-201410211230386761.html Sudan's Bashir to seek re-election in 2015] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/10/sudan-bashir-seek-re-election-2015-201410211230386761.html |date=20191202195246 }} Al Jazeera, 21 October 2014</ref>。15个其他候选人登记参选。<ref name=BBC/>

尽管有44个政党提出候选人，但大多数反对党抵制了选举。而全国大会党在30%的选区没有推出候选人，让其他政党获得一些议员。<ref name=BBC>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-32249860 Sudan election: Will Bashir be snubbed by his people?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-32249860 |date=20150416053349 }} BBC News, 13 April 2015</ref>

[[非洲联盟|非洲联盟]]、[[阿拉伯联盟|阿拉伯联盟]]、[[东部和南部非洲共同市场|东部和南部非洲共同市场]]（COMESA）、[[政府间发展机构|政府间发展机构]]（IGAD）、[[伊斯兰合作组织|伊斯兰合作组织]]（OIC）派出了选举观察员；<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oic-oci.org/oicv2/topic/?t_id=9996&ref=3961&lan=en|title=OIC observes Presidential and Legislative Elections in the Sudan|last1=|first1=|last2=|first2=|date=21 April 2015|website=|publisher=OIC|access-date=28 April 2015}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>还有来自[[中国|中国]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]和[[土耳其|土耳其]]的观察员。<ref name="summon"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://sudanow.info.sd/west-unhappy-about-the-elections-what-do-others-say/ |title=West Unhappy About the Elections: What Do Others Say? |last1=al-Haj Hassan |first1=Abdullah |date=25 April 2015 |website= |publisher=Sudan News Agency |access-date=28 April 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213115444/http://sudanow.info.sd/west-unhappy-about-the-elections-what-do-others-say/ |archive-date=2019-02-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

非洲联盟由尼日利亚前总统[[奥卢塞贡·奥巴桑乔|奥卢塞贡·奥巴桑乔]]率领，观察团表示“满意和平的投票”并指出国家“仍面临民主建设和民族和解的严重挑战”。它得出结论说，“结果……将反映苏丹选民的意志的表达”。<ref>{{cite press release|last=|first=|date=16 April 2015|title=AUEOM to Sudan|url=http://pa.au.int/en/sites/default/files/Press%20Statement%20of%20the%20AUEOM%20in%20Sudan_0.pdf|location=|publisher=African Union|agency=|access-date=2015-04-28}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

COMESA 观察团表示“一般环境内大选组织得非常和平”，并称赞苏丹人民。它还指出，担心“大选被几个反对党抵制”。<ref>{{cite press release |last= |first= |date=April 2015 |title=COMESA Election Observer Mission to the General Elections in the Republic of the Sudan |url=http://www.comesa.int/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1480:comesa-election-observer-mission-to-the-general-elections-in-the-republic-of-the-sudan-april-2015&catid=5:latest-news&Itemid=41 |location= |publisher=COMESA |agency= |access-date=2015-04-28 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310235427/http://www.comesa.int/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1480:comesa-election-observer-mission-to-the-general-elections-in-the-republic-of-the-sudan-april-2015&catid=5:latest-news&Itemid=41 }}</ref>

