ll-not-affect-polls-.html |title=Sudan’s Bashir says foreign criticism will not affect polls |last1= |first1= |last2= |first2= |date=24 April 2015 |website= |publisher=al Arabiya |access-date=28 April 2015 |archive-date=2020-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200509083257/https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/africa/2015/04/24/Sudan-s-Bashir-says-foreign-criticism-will-not-affect-polls-.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

